{{Infobox Union |name= Målareförbundet |country= [[Sweden]] |affiliation= [[Swedish Trade Union Confederation|LO]] |members= 20,000 |full_name= Swedish Painters' Union |native_name= Svenska Målareförbundet |image= [[Image:Svenska Målareförbundet (logo).png]] |founded=1887 |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Stockholm]], Sweden |people= [[Lars-Åke Lundin]], president |website= [http://www.malareforbundet.a.se www.malareforbundet.a.se] |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Swedish Painters' Union''' is a [[trade union]] in [[Sweden]]. It has a membership of 20,000 and is affiliated with the [[Swedish Trade Union Confederation]].
